parameters: Did you run away from the war, you coward!

Are you being controlled by a monster or something? I'm scared to
approach....
No way!!! Don't say such things!!

Hayato: My home, my friends, my family, they've all been taken
away from me!!

Hayato: Don't be cruel to a child who has come this far carrying
so much! I won't allow it!!
Hayato: That includes you, the adventurer over there.
Hayato, please empathize more with people's pain!!
Wh-what the... Hayato, we were just playing around....

I-I'm sorry.... The truth is, this isn't really the place for a
barrier....
\F[36]\AA[F]... It's okay. Everyone must think I'm a nuisance.

\F[36]\AA[F]I ran away from the monsters, you know? Their
pursuers might come here....

\F[39]\AA[F]I-I... I'm just a weak human too... There are times
when I get hurt...

Hayato, without saying a word, hugs the trembling girl and
strokes her head.
It's okay, it's okay.... You can stay here as long as you want.

You, who have come this far without being crushed by painful
experiences, are stronger than anyone in Variente.

So, please lay down your burdens and stay here forever. We need
someone like you.

I-I-I-I'm sorry!! I touched you without any warning...! I
just.....

\F[3]\AA[F]... *sniffle*. It's okay. You're pretty bad at
flirting, after all.
Anyone who flirts in a situation like this is a villain.
\F[17]\AA[F](I was joking, but she responded with a serious face)
Celia, I've made up my mind.

I will protect you... so that you, Celia, can live here without
any problems. So that you don't have to live in fear...

I also lost my brother in the war... I want to do everything I
can for you, Celia, seriously.
Of course, I'll do as I please!

Also, you can just call me by my name. We're the same age after
all...
(From now on, we're going to become closer...)
